    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An Inhuman Chain of Command</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are the leader of a powerful strike team sent where containment has already failed. Experience intense third-person, over-the-shoulder action with grounded gunplay and brutal melee combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/5adfac4162b9b2753e5cb23ec9e1f7de.poster.avif?t=1771871566\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/5adfac4162b9b2753e5cb23ec9e1f7de.webm?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/5adfac4162b9b2753e5cb23ec9e1f7de.mp4?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Authority Is Your Weapon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command your squad to maximize efficiency under stress. Order them to follow and protect you, hold positions to secure key areas, or focus priority targets with lethal precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/4d1b823c7c32479d07c9014d86e30a55.poster.avif?t=1771871566\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/4d1b823c7c32479d07c9014d86e30a55.webm?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/4d1b823c7c32479d07c9014d86e30a55.mp4?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Concrete, Silence, Secrets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your employer’s facility has suffered a catastrophic security breach. Descend into sealed corridors to uncover what went wrong - and clean up the mess. Collect samples, erase evidence, and secure containment at any cost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/aceef29beb8441c658a9ae813ac50443.poster.avif?t=1771871566\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/aceef29beb8441c658a9ae813ac50443.webm?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/aceef29beb8441c658a9ae813ac50443.mp4?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Living, Mutating Hostiles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face intelligent, physically simulated enemies that dodge, adapt and mutate mid-combat. The deeper you descend, the more grotesque and dangerous they become.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/e9cb1a5a7460c99f1c443d115d0f62d1.poster.avif?t=1771871566\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/e9cb1a5a7460c99f1c443d115d0f62d1.webm?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/e9cb1a5a7460c99f1c443d115d0f62d1.mp4?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage Your Supplies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resources are finite, and waste is punished. Loot the facility, craft what you need, and ration ammunition carefully. Your survival depends on managing both your own supplies and those of your squad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/06f237c8cd4874c1aa7fd9d4add8cdd9.poster.avif?t=1771871566\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/06f237c8cd4874c1aa7fd9d4add8cdd9.webm?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/06f237c8cd4874c1aa7fd9d4add8cdd9.mp4?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arsenal of Control</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight back with an arsenal of over 10 firearms, crafted using futuristic tech. Deploy grenades to break formations. Use a compact recon drone to scan ahead, revealing threats, loot and most importantly: Your way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/2ad72f0ac9d2cb3c734ccd8d26a41880.poster.avif?t=1771871566\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/2ad72f0ac9d2cb3c734ccd8d26a41880.webm?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/2ad72f0ac9d2cb3c734ccd8d26a41880.mp4?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Truth Is Fragmented</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The facility hides more than countless corpses and contagious biomass. Piece together what happened - and what escaped containment - through exploration and hard evidence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/94036ca30171f034bb31344e0cd6838a.poster.avif?t=1771871566\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/94036ca30171f034bb31344e0cd6838a.webm?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198250/extras/94036ca30171f034bb31344e0cd6838a.mp4?t=1771871566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
